1.0.name: wordpress/infoway
1.0.description: InfoWay is a Clean, Simple & Elegant Responsive WordPress Theme built by InkThemes.com. You can use Infoway Theme to build beautiful website for your business site and your blog. The core of Infoway Theme is its simplicity to Install and use, you can customize and use your own logo, texts and images easily using the in-built Themes Options Panel. InfoWay Theme support widgets in sidebar and footer, which gives you infinite ways to customize your site. The Theme comes with elegant color scheme which looks good for different types of website. You would definitely love to create your website using InfoWay.
